drm/amdgpu/display: Replace CONFIG_DRM_AMD_DC_DCN1_0 with CONFIG_X86

Allowing CONFIG_DRM_AMD_DC_DCN1_0 to be disabled on X86 was an
opportunity for display with Raven Ridge accidentally not working.

